MyBroadband has launched its 2018 DStv and Netflix Survey. The survey looks at what DStv, Netflix, and other customers think about what’s on offer in the market, and comes at a time when there is a lot of action in the entertainment sector. This includes MultiChoice, DStv’s owners, stating that Netflix must be subjected to the same regulations as local broadcasters, and pay tax in South Africa. The DStv and Netflix Survey will take 1 minute to complete, is completely anonymous, and you can win cool prizes. Once you have completed the survey, you can enter the awesome MyBroadband giveaway. Please say “Done” in this thread once you have completed the survey to enter the giveaway competition. The prizes are: